<SYNC Start=683605><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;

<SYNC Start=714588><P Class=KRCC>
우시마타님
<SYNC Start=716150><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;

<SYNC Start=716692><P Class=KRCC>
부인께는 죄송하지만<br>
