<SYNC Start=940722><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;

<SYNC Start=948616><P Class=KRCC>
우시마타님
<SYNC Start=950539><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;

<SYNC Start=954147><P Class=KRCC>
이라코 세이겐
<SYNC Start=955879><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;

<SYNC Start=956140><P Class=KRCC>
